cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.SD 

This paper deals with machine translation and semantic web techniques, which are closely related to the fields of computational linguistics (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of ontology-based approaches also suggests a connection to information retrieval (cs.IR) and knowledge representation (cs.LG). Finally, the focus on improving the accuracy of machine translation aligns with the sub-category of software engineering (cs.SD).
